playstore_details.title: SBI Secure OTP
playstore_details.description:
SBI Secure OTP is an OTP generation App for verifying transactions done through SBI Internet Banking and Yono Lite App. 

The application will replace the need for receiving the OTP for INB transactions via SMS. OTP can be generated using the application after completion of registration process. The application will generate Online OTP with Internet connectivity ON.

User can generate Online OTP after login to the application. 

User can click on the de-register option provided in the "Settings" menu within the application. Alternatively visit Onlinesbi and go to "Profile>> High Security Option" and deregister the SBI Secure OTP App from there to complete the de-registration process.

Please note that after de-registration of the app, user will start receiving the OTP in registered mobile number with Internet Banking.

One time registration with your Internet Banking credentials is required for using the App. Service provider independent, hassle free OTP service is now available to customer.

For more details please visit, https://mobilityretail.sbi/sbijava/mobile/sbsecure_otp_app_faq.html
